body:
@adamjstewart 

Excising convoluted brittle code that was frequently breaking.

The filter_file HDF5 hack was unfortunately going off the rails even though it previously seemed to work. HDF5 detection is working robustly in QE 6.4.1, but only with MPI enabled. HDF5 detection is still having problems with the serial QE. I am working with the QE developers to get it fixed in the native configure, so we don't have to run these filter_files. Less headache for the people who maintain this package.
